summary: This document appears to be a deposit account opening application for Deutsche Asset & Wealth Management. It outlines various account types, customer identification policies, and terms and conditions for account holders. The document emphasizes compliance with anti-money laundering regulations and the responsibilities of account holders regarding their tax obligations.
keyFacts: The document is a deposit account opening application for Deutsche Asset & Wealth Management.
It includes various account types such as checking accounts, money market deposits, and certificates of deposit.
There is a strong emphasis on compliance with anti-money laundering laws and customer identification policies.
The document outlines the responsibilities of account holders regarding tax obligations and regulatory reporting.
No specific individuals are named in the document, but it references the need for personal identification and documentation.
